Shadowgate employs recognition system that hides your name from other
players and allows them to remember you by the name you present in
character, when meeting others. However, try to avoid the next things:

 1. Names that are know in books, games, movies, mythology are not allowed.
 2. Names that are dictionary words or combinations of words are not allowed.
 3. You can not use the same name to reclaim history of another character.

